Hail and well met fellow Bard of Norrath. I am new to Bardic practices and
was looking for help in developing my bardic skills, speech and knowledge in
this aspect. I am a Lev 9 Half-Elf Bard on the Fennin Ro server. I am open
to all suggestions, opinions, critisiszm (Man I need spelling help too :)

Thanks and well met to all........

Koden
Bard of The League of Swords
Qeynos Fennin Ro server.
